snippet.title: Seishun Quiz: Colorful Highschool playthrough 01
snippet.description:
Seishun Quiz: Colorful Highschool is an arcade game released in 2003 by Namco.
In various aspects, it resembles a lot to THE iDOLM@STER, including the same character designer Toshiyuki Kubooka (Lunar, Giant Robo...).

The girls are:
Blue hair: Miku Kanzaki (voice: Megumi Nasu)
Blonde hair: Ayaka Kujou (voice: Chiaki Takahashi)
Orange hair: Megumi Shishido (voice: Chiwa Saitou)
Dark pink hair: Marie Takamura (voice: Kana Ueda)

Official site: http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/am/vg/colorfulhighschool/

The video was uploaded in Nico Nico Douga by the user Misokatsu (Gorira★Ｐ).
http://www.nicovideo.jp/mylist/922542
